      <title>印度寻求海外锂加工帮助以避免依赖中国</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-seeks-overseas-help-lithium-processing-avoid-relying-china-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[四位知情人士表示，印度正在与多个国家进行谈判，寻求锂加工方面的技术帮助合作伙伴，以支持其新兴的锂开采和电动汽车行业，并避免依赖中国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-seeks-overseas-help-lithium-processing-avoid-relying-china-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 09:57:08 GMT</pubDate>
